<doc id="1035758" wikidata="Q536845" url="?curid=1035758" title="Advanced Aviation">
<text>Advanced Aviation was a manufacturer of ultralight aircraft in kit form based in Orlando, Florida. It marketed designs by HighCraft AeroMarine under licence.

==Aircraft types==

